<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help | Tick-Track</title>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/webhome.css"> -->
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1536545.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #c0c0c0;
        }

        /* Help Section */
        .help-section {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: rgba(43, 42, 42, 0.6); /* Transparent background */
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #f2f2f2;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .help-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .help-section h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ddd;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .help-section p,
        .help-section ul li {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .help-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .help-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .help-button .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .help-button .btn:hover {
            background-color: #34497d;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .help-section {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .help-section h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .help-section h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .help-section p,
            .help-section ul li {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>Tick-Track</h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/help">Help</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="help-section">
                <h2>Help Center</h2>
                <p>Find answers to your questions about your account and login issues.</p>
                
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Creating an Account</h3>
                    <p>If you are having trouble creating an account, ensure that you are using a valid email address and that your password meets the required criteria.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Logging In</h3>
                    <p>If you're unable to log in, please check the following:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Ensure that you are using the correct email and password.</li>
                        <li>Make sure your Caps Lock is off.</li>
                        <li>If you've forgotten your password, use the "Forgot Password?" link on the login page.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Password Recovery</h3>
                    <p>If you've forgotten your password, click on the "Forgot Password?" link on the login page and follow the instructions to reset it.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Account Issues</h3>
                    <p>If you encounter any issues with your account, such as locked accounts or incorrect information, please contact our support team.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Tick-Track. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


